的社交媒體訊息中，內容均提及電油等字眼，尤其是第三被告的WhatsApp訊息，認為兩人對涉案物品不陌生，一定知悉物品是用於製造汽油彈，但他們仍選擇逗留在單位內，認為他們有意願參加遊行，並知悉有人將會在遊行中使用汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n至於第四及第五被告，控方承認沒有直接證據證明她們知道有人會使用汽油彈，但兩人在單位出現並留宿，看到涉案物品、亦即她們知悉即將參與的遊行中有人會使用這些汽油彈，參與暴動。至於第六被告，控方則沒有進一步補充。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/DVDU5AVOEJBMJM3BMLVBXGM4EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2FDVDU5AVOEJBMJM3BMLVBXGM4EU%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=cf075c12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2FDVDU5AVOEJBMJM3BMLVBXGM4EU%2F&h=e5207423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/DVDU5AVOEJBMJM3BMLVBXGM4EU/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"馬立道學野啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"出句聲都唔敢啦佢，鹿道立<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治閹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f408977af269fa15c8190b8bd3c87819c61ae0d3","tid":2336094,"uid":152104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"沈小民都紅紅地，咁都頂佢地唔順"},{"pid":"0927a3f86b1d88b8070d89625d33e7e2c04a6201","tid":2336094,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a1338eec4569aa29fa7386b9a297b0a5e85c4a","tid":2336094,"uid":357710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"109af5cc01ebf0a3a726af0a29000dff10a0019c","tid":2336094,"uid":6058,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"d5dc778606c7d1edb73edf4b84fa603ba61d5217","tid":2336094,"uid":41771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"律政司有得投訴架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"我就係搵緊方法去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"可以打信去佢上級投訴工作表現(檢控質素)欠佳&nbsp;,&nbsp;但都是由律政司另一TEAM處理"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"直接D，投訴去大律師公會，話他incompetent同違反大律師守則，釘牌大獲過等律政司作故仔包庇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkba.org/content/code-conduct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkba.org%2Fcontent%2Fcode-conduct&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=fb4ba0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkba.org/content/code-conduct</a><br />\nDuties When Prosecuting a Person Accused of a Crime<br />\n<br />\n10.65       Prosecuting Counsel should not regard himself as appearing for a party.<br />\n<br />\n10.66       It is not the duty of Prosecuting Counsel to obtain a conviction by all means at his command but rather to lay before the Court or the jury fairly and impartially the whole of the facts which comprise the case for the prosecution and to assist the Court on or, to see that the jury are properly instructed in, all matters of law applicable to the case."}]}